OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FThree 23-year-olds explain to Good
OL,7,FMorning Britain why finding a job is
OL,8,Fso tough for young people despite
OL,9,Fhaving decent qualifications
OL,11,FA 23-year-old data analyst with a
OL,12,Ffirst-class postgraduate degree in
OL,13,Fcomputer science was left increasingly
OL,14,Fdemoralised after receiving 500
OL,15,Frejections before finally landing a
OL,16,Fjob.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FTheo Dal Pozzo told ITV's Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain that some roles he applied for
OL,8,Fattracted more than 1,000 applicants,
OL,9,Fwhich chipped away at his hopes of
OL,10,Ffinding work during his year-long
OL,11,Fsearch.
OL,13,FHe suggested his successful
OL,14,Fapplication may have been helped by
OL,15,Fspeaking publicly about the lack of
OL,16,Fopportunities for young people and by
OL,17,Fwriting a viral LinkedIn post about
OL,18,Fthe bleak jobs market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FNew figures from the Office for
OL,7,FNational Statistics (ONS) show
OL,8,F1,012,000 young people, aged 16-24,
OL,9,Fwere Neet (not in employment,
OL,10,Feducation or training) between January
OL,11,Fand March 2026 ` a 55,000 increase
OL,12,Fcompared with the previous quarter.
OL,14,FThe problem could get worse, according
OL,15,Fto a government-commissioned review,
OL,16,Fled by Alan Milburn, which warns the
OL,17,Ftotal number could rise to 1.25
OL,18,Fmillion in the next five years.
OL,20,F"Getting a job was a job in itself,"
OL,21,FDal Pozzo told GMB.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FHe said he didn't feel that he got a
OL,7,Ffair hearing when putting out
OL,8,Fapplications.
OL,10,F"One of the main things is that AI is
OL,11,Frising and cutting out a lot of junior
OL,12,Froles," he said. "So, I think there
OL,13,Fare a lot less junior roles available
OL,14,Fnow than there were previously.
OL,16,F"I was doing everything right and I
OL,17,Fwasn't getting results."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FDal Pozzo suspects that one of the
OL,7,Fmain issues he faced was that he did
OL,8,Fnot have any work experience before
OL,9,Fhis first job.
OL,11,F"The master's is important but I think
OL,12,Fwork experience is just as important,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FRejection after rejection made Dal
OL,16,FPozzo feel depressed, but he adopted a
OL,17,Fway of thinking that he said helped
OL,18,Fhim through his challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,F"It was always going to be a no until
OL,7,Fit was a yes of having a job or not,
OL,8,Fright, so I kind of changed my mindset
OL,9,Finto measuring things instead of by
OL,10,F'do I have a job, do I not have a
OL,11,Fjob?' to, 'have I reached out, have I
OL,12,Fsent a cover letter in, have I done
OL,13,Fsome outreach?'."
OL,15,FAmong three young graduates who spoke
OL,16,Fto Good Morning Britain on Thursday
OL,17,Fmorning, Dal Pozzo was one of the
OL,18,Flucky ones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FOlivia McLaren, also aged 23, who has
OL,7,Fa biomedical degree and a Master of
OL,8,FResearch at Aston University, has been
OL,9,Flooking for a job for months and has
OL,10,Fonly had one interview so far, to
OL,11,Fwhich she got a "maybe".
OL,13,F"It's an administrator role. It's not
OL,14,Feven a science dream job. I just need
OL,15,Fto get a job... I have my foot in the
OL,16,Fdoor. It's the first stepping stone,
OL,17,Fbut I've still got a long way."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FLike Dal Pozzo, McLaren says AI is
OL,7,Fpartly to blame for the challenges
OL,8,Ffaced by young people looking for
OL,9,Fentry-level jobs.
OL,11,FShe mentioned the ATS (Applicant
OL,12,FTracking System) used to automate and
OL,13,Fspeed up recruitment processes,
OL,14,Fsuggesting that "if you don't have
OL,15,Fcertain specific keywords, then you're
OL,16,Fjust dismissed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FMcLaren says that after speaking to
OL,7,Fthe DWP-funded Connect to Work
OL,8,Fprogramme and signing on to Universal
OL,9,FCredit, she was advised to look at the
OL,10,Fjob description and input the same
OL,11,Fwords used in her CV.
OL,13,F"Before I knew that there was like a
OL,14,Fproblem going on in the country, I
OL,15,Freally thought it was a personal
OL,16,Fproblem; my confidence dropped," she
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,F"I started to believe I wasn't
OL,7,Fintelligent enough to do the job. And
OL,8,FI think young people's confidence is
OL,9,Fjust getting destroyed right now."
OL,11,FShana Fatahali, who has a Level 2
OL,12,Fqualification in health and social
OL,13,Fcare and another in autism, has been
OL,14,Fsearching for a job since 2021.
OL,16,F"I would have loved to have gone into
OL,17,Ffurther education, but with having a
OL,18,Fdaughter who has taken up most of my
OL,19,Ftime and my responsibilities lay with
OL,20,Fher at the moment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FLack of access to childcare in her
OL,7,Farea is another issue, she says, with
OL,8,Fpeople having to wait a year for a
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,F"In school, we were always told that
OL,12,Fwith certain qualifications, when you
OL,13,Fgo to college, that you'd be able to
OL,14,Fdo certain jobs and progress from
OL,15,Fthere," she told GMB.
OL,17,F"But that wasn't the case for myself.
OL,18,FI was told to go back to college and
OL,19,Fthen to apply for university, and
OL,20,Fthat's not a route that all young
OL,21,Fpeople want to take."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779995468
OL,3,CRejected 500 times: young people
OL,4,Cfighting to get their first job
OL,6,FReflecting on how this affected her
OL,7,Foutlook, Fatahali, also aged 23, said:
OL,8,F"You sort of put yourself into the
OL,9,Fmindset... 'why is nothing happening
OL,10,Fto me?' Like you feel stuck.
OL,12,F"I would never feel like I would be
OL,13,Fenvious of other people. I'm happy
OL,14,Fthat other people have got jobs. It's
OL,15,Falmost a boost to want to get a job
OL,16,Fand look for a job.
OL,18,F"But, you know, we can look for jobs,
OL,19,Fbut it's about whether jobs want to
OL,20,Ftake on young people."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
